  "keyFeatures": [
    "Upload and analyze PDF or text files for AI-generated content",
    "Three AI model options (SVM, RoBERTa, MLP) with different speed/accuracy tradeoffs",
    "Real-time progress indicators during analysis",
    "Confidence scores and visual result display",
    "PDF text extraction with normalization",
    "Drag-and-drop file upload support",
    "Responsive design with mobile support"
